---
name: deploy
description: Build and prepare for BGA deployment
---

Prepare the Wayfarers game for BGA deployment:

1. Run the full build process: `npm run build`
2. Check for any build errors in TypeScript, SCSS, or material generation
3. Show git status to see which files have changed
4. Check for spelling mistakes and issues in changed code

Do not create a git commit unless explicitly asked.
